title: Take
occurrences: - What's going on? - Take a guess.
- But I did a triple knot this time. - (Shit) All right, just take your foot out. Come on!
No, honey your feet, take them off the coffee table
Why don't you take some responsibility for yourself? Some accountability?
Don't you at least want to take the tags off? -No way! I'm saving them for school!
- We'll drop you off and then Jessie and I will come back. - No, you take the car, I can walk back.
- I want to go with Dad! My Moto-Father - I'll take him with me if you want.
- You take me! - Give me 10 minutes!
